@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam usecaseFontSize 10

left to right direction

actor "Project Lead" as PL
actor "Team Member" as TM
actor "Viewer/Stakeholder" as VS

usecase "Xem Timeline\nview" as UC_Timeline
usecase "Load issues\ntheo khoảng thời gian" as UC_LoadRange
usecase "Hiển thị issue\ntrên timeline" as UC_DisplayTimeline
usecase "Zoom in/out\ntimeline" as UC_Zoom
usecase "Filter theo\nfilter criteria" as UC_FilterTimeline

PL --> UC_Timeline
TM --> UC_Timeline
VS --> UC_Timeline

UC_LoadRange .up.> UC_Timeline : <<include>>
UC_DisplayTimeline .up.> UC_Timeline : <<include>>
UC_Zoom .up.> UC_Timeline : <<extend>>
UC_FilterTimeline .up.> UC_Timeline : <<extend>>

note right of UC_DisplayTimeline
  Issues hiển thị dưới dạng
  horizontal bars với:
  - Issue key và title
  - Start date và due date
  - Progress indicator
  - Dependencies giữa issues
end note

note bottom of UC_Zoom
  Users có thể:
  - Zoom để xem theo ngày/tuần/tháng
  - Scroll timeline ngang
  - Drag to pan
end note

@enduml
